tplinkl2BridgeMIB.name: tplinkl2BridgeMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tplinkl2BridgeMIB.description: This MIB module contain a collection of managed objects for l2 table address.

fdbDynMacNew.name: fdbDynMacNew
fdbDynMacNew.description: The switch has learned a new dynamic address.

fdbStaticMacNew.name: fdbStaticMacNew
fdbStaticMacNew.description: The switch has learned a new static address.

fdbFilterMacNew.name: fdbFilterMacNew
fdbFilterMacNew.description: The switch has learned a new filter address.

fdbMacTableFull.name: fdbMacTableFull
fdbMacTableFull.description: The switch's Address Table is full!

fdbMacMaxLearnedNumExceed.name: fdbMacMaxLearnedNumExceed
fdbMacMaxLearnedNumExceed.description: The l2BridgeManageStaticPort has learned the maximum number of address that it can learn.

fdbMacLearnModeChange.name: fdbMacLearnModeChange
fdbMacLearnModeChange.description: The l2BridgeManageDynPort has opened its portSecurity, and changes its learning mode.

tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlTable.name: tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlTable
tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlTable.description: A list of static mac address entries.

tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlEntry.name: tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlEntry
tpl2BridgeManageStaticAddrCtrlEntry.description: The static address can be added or removed manually, independent of the aging time. In the stable networks, the static MAC address entries can facilitate the switch to reduce broadcast packets and enhance the efficiency of packets forwarding remarkably.

tpl2BridgeManageStaticVlanId.name: tpl2BridgeManageStaticVlanId
tpl2BridgeManageStaticVlanId.description: The corresponding VLAN ID of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageStaticPort.name: tpl2BridgeManageStaticPort
tpl2BridgeManageStaticPort.description: The corresponding Port number of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageStaticStatus.name: tpl2BridgeManageStaticStatus
tpl2BridgeManageStaticStatus.description: The following values are states: these values may be used as follow: active(1),if the entry is being used. createAndGo(4),creat a new entry destroy(6),destory the entry.

tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlAgingTime.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlAgingTime
tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlAgingTime.description: Configure aging time for the dynamic address.Set 0 to disable auto aging.

tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlTable.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlTable
tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlTable.description: A list of dynamic MAC address entries.

tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlEntry.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlEntry
tpl2BridgeManageDynAddrCtrlEntry.description: The dynamic address can be generated by the auto-learning mechanism of the switch. The Dynamic Address Table can update automatically by auto-learning or aging out the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageDynVlanId.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynVlanId
tpl2BridgeManageDynVlanId.description: Displays the corresponding VLAN ID of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageDynPort.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynPort
tpl2BridgeManageDynPort.description: The corresponding port number of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageDynAgeStatus.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynAgeStatus
tpl2BridgeManageDynAgeStatus.description: The Aging Status of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageDynStatus.name: tpl2BridgeManageDynStatus
tpl2BridgeManageDynStatus.description: active(1)......It's should be enable when the MAC address is exist. bind(4)........Bind the dynamic MAC entry. destroy(6).....Delete the dynamic MAC entry.

tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlTable.name: tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlTable
tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlTable.description: A list of filter MAC address entries.

tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlEntry.name: tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlEntry
tpl2BridgeManageFilterCtrlEntry.description: The filtering address is to forbid the undesired package to be forwarded. The filtering address can be added or removed manually, independent of the aging time.

tpl2BridgeManageFilterStatus.name: tpl2BridgeManageFilterStatus
tpl2BridgeManageFilterStatus.description: The following values are states: these values may be used as follow: active(1),if the entry is being used. createAndGo(4),not being used destroy(6),destory the entry.

VlanSecEntryStatus.name: VlanSecEntryStatus
VlanSecEntryStatus.description: The status of a table entry.

tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecurityTable.name: tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecurityTable
tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecurityTable.description: A list of Fdb vlan security control entries.

tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecEntry.name: tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecEntry
tpl2BridgeManagevlanSecEntry.description: The mac vlan security entry is used to set vlan mac address learning config.

tpFdbVlanSecurityVid.name: tpFdbVlanSecurityVid
tpFdbVlanSecurityVid.description: The vlan id of this entry.

tpFdbVlanSecurityMaxLearned.name: tpFdbVlanSecurityMaxLearned
tpFdbVlanSecurityMaxLearned.description: The max learned limit mac of this vlan security entry.

tpFdbVlanSecurityRowStatus.name: tpFdbVlanSecurityRowStatus
tpFdbVlanSecurityRowStatus.description: The status column has four defined values: - 'disable(0)', this entry is exist but invalid; - 'drop(1)', packets with other source mac will be drop when exceed max learned mac; - 'forward(2)', packets with other source mac can be forwarded when exceed max learned mac; - 'createRequest(3)', which is supplied by a management station wishing to create a new instance of a conceptual row and to have its status automatically set to forward(1), making it available for using by the managed device; - 'destory(4)', which is supplied by a management station wishing to delete all of the instances associated with an existing conceptual row.

tpl2BridgeManageNotificationGlobalStatus.name: tpl2BridgeManageNotificationGlobalStatus
tpl2BridgeManageNotificationGlobalStatus.description: The mac address notification global status.

tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTableFullSta.name: tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTableFullStatus
tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTableFullSta.description: The mac address notification when the table is full.

tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTable.name: tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTable
tpl2BridgeManageNotificationTable.description: A list of port MAC address Notification setting.

tpl2BridgeManageNotificationCtrlEntry.name: tpl2BridgeManageNotificationCtrlEntry
tpl2BridgeManageNotificationCtrlEntry.description: The dynamic address can be generated by the auto-learning mechanism of the switch. The Dynamic Address Table can update automatically by auto-learning or aging out the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManagePortIndex.name: tpl2BridgeManagePortIndex
tpl2BridgeManagePortIndex.description: This object indicates the port number.

tpl2BridgeManageLrnModeChg.name: tpl2BridgeManageLrnModeChg
tpl2BridgeManageLrnModeChg.description: Displays the Learn mode change of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageExceedMaxLrn.name: tpl2BridgeManageExceedMaxLrn
tpl2BridgeManageExceedMaxLrn.description: Displays the exceed max learned of the MAC address.

tpl2BridgeManageNewMacLrn.name: tpl2BridgeManageNewMacLrn
tpl2BridgeManageNewMacLrn.description: Displays the new mac learned of the MAC address.
